Gareth Bale: Wales and Real Madrid star gets engaged

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Wales and Real Madrid star Gareth Bale has got engaged to his long-term girlfriend Emma Rhys-Jones.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 27-year-old, who celebrated his birthday on Saturday, made the announcement on Twitter.
The couple, from Cardiff, have two daughters.
